STEP 7: Run App Locally (Shows GAE Launcher Concept)
In Bash console, run the app directly:
bashcd ~/app1
python main.py
You'll see:
* Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000
* Press CTRL+C to quit
This is exactly what GAE Launcher used to do — run the app locally before deploying. ✅
